        <updateDate>2019-09-09T14:57:38Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Creating Access to Rehabilitation for Every Senior Act of 2017 or the CARES Act of 2017</b></p> <p>This bill eliminates the three-day prior-hospitalization requirement for Medicare coverage of certain skilled-nursing-facilities services. The Medicare Payment Advisory Commission must study the cost of impact of such elimination.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
